comment:
* This interface defines the constants that are used by the classes
 * which manipulate ZIP files.
 *
 * @author      David Connelly
 * @since 1.1

variables.name: LOCHDR
variables.comment: * Local file (LOC) header size in bytes (including signature).

variables.name: EXTHDR
variables.comment: * Extra local (EXT) header size in bytes (including signature).

variables.name: CENHDR
variables.comment: * Central directory (CEN) header size in bytes (including signature).

variables.name: ENDHDR
variables.comment: * End of central directory (END) header size in bytes (including signature).

variables.name: LOCVER
variables.comment: * Local file (LOC) header version needed to extract field offset.

variables.name: LOCFLG
variables.comment: * Local file (LOC) header general purpose bit flag field offset.

variables.name: LOCHOW
variables.comment: * Local file (LOC) header compression method field offset.

variables.name: LOCTIM
variables.comment: * Local file (LOC) header modification time field offset.

variables.name: LOCCRC
variables.comment: * Local file (LOC) header uncompressed file crc-32 value field offset.

variables.name: LOCSIZ
variables.comment: * Local file (LOC) header compressed size field offset.

variables.name: LOCLEN
variables.comment: * Local file (LOC) header uncompressed size field offset.

variables.name: LOCNAM
variables.comment: * Local file (LOC) header filename length field offset.

variables.name: LOCEXT
variables.comment: * Local file (LOC) header extra field length field offset.

variables.name: EXTCRC
variables.comment: * Extra local (EXT) header uncompressed file crc-32 value field offset.

variables.name: EXTSIZ
variables.comment: * Extra local (EXT) header compressed size field offset.

variables.name: EXTLEN
variables.comment: * Extra local (EXT) header uncompressed size field offset.

variables.name: CENVEM
variables.comment: * Central directory (CEN) header version made by field offset.

variables.name: CENVER
variables.comment: * Central directory (CEN) header version needed to extract field offset.

variables.name: CENFLG
variables.comment: * Central directory (CEN) header encrypt, decrypt flags field offset.

variables.name: CENHOW
variables.comment: * Central directory (CEN) header compression method field offset.

variables.name: CENTIM
variables.comment: * Central directory (CEN) header modification time field offset.

variables.name: CENCRC
variables.comment: * Central directory (CEN) header uncompressed file crc-32 value field offset.

variables.name: CENSIZ
variables.comment: * Central directory (CEN) header compressed size field offset.

variables.name: CENLEN
variables.comment: * Central directory (CEN) header uncompressed size field offset.

variables.name: CENNAM
variables.comment: * Central directory (CEN) header filename length field offset.

variables.name: CENEXT
variables.comment: * Central directory (CEN) header extra field length field offset.

variables.name: CENCOM
variables.comment: * Central directory (CEN) header comment length field offset.

variables.name: CENDSK
variables.comment: * Central directory (CEN) header disk number start field offset.

variables.name: CENATT
variables.comment: * Central directory (CEN) header internal file attributes field offset.

variables.name: CENATX
variables.comment: * Central directory (CEN) header external file attributes field offset.

variables.name: CENOFF
variables.comment: * Central directory (CEN) header LOC header offset field offset.

variables.name: ENDSUB
variables.comment: * End of central directory (END) header number of entries on this disk field offset.

variables.name: ENDTOT
variables.comment: * End of central directory (END) header total number of entries field offset.

variables.name: ENDSIZ
variables.comment: * End of central directory (END) header central directory size in bytes field offset.

variables.name: ENDOFF
variables.comment: * End of central directory (END) header offset for the first CEN header field offset.

variables.name: ENDCOM
variables.comment: * End of central directory (END) header zip file comment length field offset.
